ile\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>Build and test native mobile apps with two simple commands</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/forge-static/img/trigger/tab-build-mobile-infographic.png\" title=\"forge build, forge run android, forge run ios\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"tab-content tab-build-web\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>Build your web app from the same codebase</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/forge-static/img/trigger/tab-build-web-infographic.png\" title=\"forge build, forge run web\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"code-block\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre>forge.request.ajax({\n\ttype: 'GET',\n\turl: 'https://api.parse.com/1/classes/my-class',\n\tdataType: 'json',\n\tsuccess: function(data, status) {\n</pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"label\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The provided web proxy &amp; JS API allows<br>your web app to make cross-domain calls</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"tab-content tab-access-users\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>Release your mobile app in the App Store / Android Market</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/forge-static/img/trigger/tab-access-mobile.png\" title=\"forge package ios, forge package android\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>Deploy your web app to Heroku</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/forge-static/img/trigger/tab-access-web.png\" title=\"forge package web\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"tab-content tab-competition active\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>How is Trigger.io better than alternatives?</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"code-block\" style>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Trigger.io does not require you to setup Eclipse or XCode<br />\n\t\t